class="card card-featured"><h1 class="card-title">
Hair Salon Website Examples - 5 In-Depth Reviews of Elegant Sites That Attract Customers</h1><div
class="card-body"><div
class="card-text card-text-prebyline">These 10 hair salon websites showcase diverse hair care services with appealing and easy-to-navigate sites on all devices.</div><div
class="card-byline"><div
class="card-byline-image">
<img
class="lazyload"
