class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="hair-nerd" class="entry-website-title">Hair Nerd</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-nerd-desktop-3840x11298-20240612.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-nerd-desktop-3840x11298-20240612.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-nerd-desktop-3840x11298-20240612.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Hair Nerd"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.hairnerd.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.hairnerd.com.au/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Paddington, Sydney, Australia</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Hair Nerd is an Australian-based hair salon specializing in alternative haircuts and color changes. The website stays true to the company's ethos with maximalist and retro-inspired design elements, such as the heading's bubble typeface and the 70s-style pastel color scheme.</p><p>The hero image of models sporting eclectic hair and makeup introduces clients to the salon's offerings, while the intermittent use of black and white imagery breaks up the colorful page sections nicely.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The use of client reviews on the home page lends credibility to the salon, while the "About" section places emphasis on the company's inclusive and sustainable practices, speaking to its target market effectively.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>While the site's pastel color scheme is fun, it does not offer sufficient contrast between the background and content sections. As such, WAVE picked up a large number of errors throughout the site.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-nerd-desktop-3840x11298-20240612.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-nerd-desktop-3840x11298-20240612.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site does a good job of conveying the salon's ethos and wide range of services, placing an emphasis on individuality and creativity with its fun style gallery of hair transformations. The online booking form is user-friendly and site navigation is relatively simple. However, many of the website's headings and CTA buttons get lost in the pastel color scheme.</p><p>According to Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the website's pages load quite fast, contributing to its high performance score of 88/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-nerd-mobile-824x12422-20240612.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-nerd-mobile-824x12422-20240612.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>Similar to the desktop version, the mobile site provides a pleasant visual experience with high-quality images and fun color accents. However, the "Menu" button towards the top of the site is not as prominent as desired, and the "Book Now" CTA button is missing from the top-right corner, hindering an optimal user experience. The website scored 56/100 in the performance category.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="mirror-mirror" class="entry-website-title">Mirror Mirror</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-mirror-mirror-20240612-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-mirror-mirror-20240612-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-mirror-mirror-20240612-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Mirror Mirror"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://mirrormirroraustin.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://mirrormirroraustin.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Austin, Texas, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Mirror Mirror is a Texas-based hair salon that offers a good selection of hair styling services. The website embraces ideas of beauty and chicness with high-quality images of the salon and its stylists, along with a sophisticated color scheme. A standout feature is the easy-to-navigate online shop for users to peruse the salon's various hair care and grooming products, offering a seamless payment and checkout experience.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website's clean page layouts allow the high-resolution images to shine, with the content-rich sections giving visitors a good overview of the salon's specialist services. The "Social feed" section on the home page is a fun addition that showcases the salon's popularity on social media.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>While the website has its telephone number at the top of the home page, its "Contact Us" button could be more prominent. WAVE picked up several instances of insufficient contrast ratios throughout the website, which could be improved for a more user-friendly experience.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-mirror-mirror-20240612-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-mirror-mirror-20240612-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website maintains the salon's elegance with polished images, while its content sections ensure visitors are well-informed of the salon's ethos and approach to hair services. A comprehensive FAQs section sheds light on the salon's booking process and pricing structure, which promotes transparency and trustworthiness. While site navigation presents no obstacles, the desktop site has slow loading times.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/mirrormirroraustin.com_Mobile-412x8191dpr2.png"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/mirrormirroraustin.com_Mobile-412x8191dpr2.png?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>For the mobile version, the site slims down nicely without losing any functionality. The content blocks are quite long and slightly overwhelming without additional images, but the text remains easily readable, adding to the website's ease of use. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the site's performance scored 36/100, likely due to its slower-than-average page loading times.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="the-parlour" class="entry-website-title">The Parlour</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-parlour-3840x8479-20240612.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-parlour-3840x8479-20240612.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-hair-parlour-3840x8479-20240612.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website The Parlour"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
