/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The mobile site presents no distinguishable navigation issues, but similar to the desktop version, some pages take a long time to load. Images and content remain refined and well-spaced, with prominent contact options accompanying a sticky hamburger menu. The site scored 49/100 in Google's PageSpeed Insight test's performance category.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
