class="entry-text"><p>The Boulevard Hair Co. is a Missouri-based franchise of hair salons dedicated to providing high-quality hair styling and barber services, as well as scalp treatments and perms. The website has an elegant yet fun appearance with dynamic color accents that complement the content-rich pages.</p><p>Clients can easily peruse the salon's services, read more about their stylists, and book an appointment from the home page. A comprehensive FAQs section ensures users are well-informed on the salon's pricing structure, booking process, and specialist services.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
