class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-you-create-a-website-for-a-hair-salon class="question">How do you create a website for a hair salon?</h3><div
class="answer"><ol><li>Consider your hair salon's style ethos, service offerings, and target market.</li><li>Think about the design elements, such as color and font, you'd like your website to have.</li><li>Use Zarla's AI-driven website builder to start designing a website.</li></ol></div></div><div
